{
  "texts": [
    "All data in the dataset are authentic inquiries from real interactions.",
    "• Medical Meadow (Han et al, 2023).",
    "The Medical Meadow dataset is an English medical instruction dataset, consisting of a total of 160K records.",
    "It has two primary sources: firstly, open-source medical NLP task datasets that have been standardized into instruction fine-tuning format, and secondly, web scraping of medical resources from the internet.",
    "The dataset encompasses a diverse range of medical domains, including biomedicine, health, bioinformatics, and more."
  ]
}